* classics such as Grendizer, Bab-el-Hara, Adnan Wa Lina, as well as the latest independent productions from the Arab World
* New shows and films added every week!!
* Drama, Cartoon, Films, Comedy and Religious programs
* Stream HQ quality for immediate viewing over 3G, 4G, 5G, WiFi
* Watch offline by downloading all your favourite shows
* Watch in your own time: Cant finish a show in one sitting? – don’t worry, just carry on where you left off when you next watch the episode/film!

How it works

* Regardless of what you decide, you can always WATCH limited previews of all your favorite shows FOR FREE
* Remember, if you’re not on WiFi, data charges may apply from your carrier – if your charges are heavy – just download the content on WiFi and you wont have to worry about charges
